metadata.name: Unravel People's ENS4
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's ENS4, which represents an inactive state of pENS4. User can participate in a new 4-digit ENS acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's ENS4 as credit. upENS4 can be claimed into pENS4 when the subscription successfully acquires a new 4-digit ENS.
